---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Layout title="Pedido Enviado">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-darkmode-body p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mb-2">¡Pedido Enviado!</h1>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Tu pedido ha sido enviado correctamente. Te hemos enviado un email de confirmación con todos los detalles.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">¿Qué sigue?</h2>
          <ul class="text-left space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-full mr-3"></span>
              Revisa tu email para la confirmación del pedido
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-full mr-3"></span>
              Nos pondremos en contacto contigo pronto para coordinar la entrega
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-full mr-3"></span>
              Si tienes alguna pregunta, no dudes en contactarnos
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a 
            href="/products" 
            class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors font-medium"
          >
            Seguir Comprando
          </a>
          <a 
            href="/" 
            class="bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-300 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors font-medium"
          >
            Volver al Inicio
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
